					<box></box>
					<textElement textAlignment="Justified">
						<font size="12"/>
					</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[This order is issued subject to recovery of all dues from the retiring person before settlement of retirement benefits and if any dues are found to be recoverable from the retired person at a later date, the person who furnished the ‘no due’ certificate will be held responsible and action will be taken against him and he will be held liable for the unrecovered amount if any.]]></text>
				</staticText>
				<staticText>
					<reportElement
						x="37"
