					<box></box>
					<textElement textAlignment="Justified">
						<font size="12"/>
					</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[Before making payment it should be ensured that all the dues to TWAD Board and others i.e. Thrift Society Recover, Bank loan recovery etc., if any are effected from his pensionary benefits.
]]></text>
				</staticText>
